| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2946 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 23baecbf-ecf0-51ce-b5fe-212eaba83fc8"
